Enum FitnessType

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:

public enum FitnessType
extends java.lang.Enum<FitnessType>

Defines which types of fitness are available to the system. This parameter is also specified by default in PopulationParameters. Different Individuals can use distinct fitness measures if they wish.

Author:
Ciarán Rowe (csr2@kent.ac.uk)
See Also:
Individual, PopulationParameters
